data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 IN CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE!!! Welcome to your new dream home!! As you step inside you’ll find an inviting, open-concept plan that boasts tons of natural light & contemporary finishes throughout. The spacious living room is the ideal for cozy evenings with a fireplace as the focal point. The kitchen is a cook’s delight, with granite countertops, SS appliances & gas stove. The bedrooms are spacious for relaxation & privacy. The primary suite includes an ensuite with a modern shower & walk-in closet, ensuring your comfort & convenience. Step outside & the backyard offers a private oasis for outdoor entertaining Living here means being part of a vibrant community with top-rated schools, parks, & thriving local scene. Explore nearby shops, restaurants, & recreational options, or take advantage of easy access to major highways for a quick commute to work or leisure activities. Don't miss your chance to make this lovely residence your own – schedule a viewing today!
